And thus begins the first chapter of the rest of his life. 
Just a few more days for my baby brothers wedding and it’s going to be a wild one. 
We deeply missed our @lifeandtimesofkiki💕 

The beautiful decor for his Grahashanti was done by my amazing friend @thecreativecompany_team who took my mood board to the next level and created a literal dreamscape for this simple puja.
